graph LR
    Controller[ODH Model Controller]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    Controller -->|core framework| KServe[KServe v0.14.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    Controller -->|orchestration| K8s[Kubernetes v1.31.0<br/>REQUIRED]
    Controller -->|ingress| OSRoute[OpenShift Route v1<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% External Dependencies (Conditional)
    Controller -->|if mesh enabled| Istio[Istio v1.23.0<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|if auth enabled| Authorino[Authorino v0.18.1<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|metrics| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator v0.64.1<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -->|if serverless| Knative[Knative Serving v0.42.2<br/>CONDITIONAL]
    Controller -.->|alternative mesh| Maistra[Red Hat Service Mesh<br/>CONDITIONAL]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Controller -->|config| DSC[DataScienceCluster CRD<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    Controller -->|references| DSCI[DSCInitialization CRD<br/>INTERNAL ODH]
    Controller -.->|optional| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>INTERNAL ODH]

    %% External Services
    Controller -->|NIM validation| NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>EXTERNAL]

    %% Integration Points (ODH Components)
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>INTERNAL ODH] -.->|manages via UI| Controller
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>INTERNAL ODH] -.->|auto-deploy models| Controller

    %% Managed Resources (Created by Controller)
    Controller -->|creates| ManagedResources[Managed Resources]

    subgraph ManagedResources[" "]
        direction TB
        Route[OpenShift Routes]
        IstioRes[Istio Resources<br/>Gateway, VirtualService,<br/>PeerAuthentication]
        AuthCfg[Authorino AuthConfig]
        NetPol[NetworkPolicies]
        RBAC[RoleBindings]
        Mon[ServiceMonitor<br/>PodMonitor]
        NIM[NIM Templates<br/>ConfigMaps, Secrets]
    end

    %% API Server Integration
    Controller -->|CRUD operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

    %% Styling
    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% Required External
    style KServe fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8s fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OSRoute fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Conditional External
    style Istio fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Authorino fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PrometheusOp fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Maistra fill:#f39c12,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Internal ODH
    style DSC fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style DSCI fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style ModelRegistry fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Dashboard fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Pipelines fill:#27ae60,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% External Services
    style NGC fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#95a5a6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Managed Resources
    style ManagedResources fill:#ecf0f1,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
